{"tid":2011040,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我要全世界同我記住今晚 2020年5月11日 母親節","createTime":"2020-05-10T17:44:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T17:52:32.000Z","uid":200641,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a0083c4c050f903ef3ab142e3501508be54d71ec","tid":2011040,"uid":200641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T17:44:46.000Z","msg":"唔知今晚有幾多人因為<br />\n<br />\n13歲記者 同媽咪講個番說話 同道歉<br />\n媽咪帶同兩個女食宵夜 但最後聲嘶力竭搵返個女<br />\n洗衣街女廁 傳出慘叫聲 <br />\n鄺議員被用膝頭壓頸 <br />\n記者被cool頸20秒<br />\n無後果咁濫捕 <br />\n蓄意傷害市民 <br />\n故亂發出告票<br />\n<br />\n而喊 <br />\n但今晚其實係 母親節 一家人慶祝<br />\n本應值得開心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n概本濫權到癲 香港行緊軍政府 凌駕法律之上<br />\n<br />\n應承我 以為每年母親節都記住班黑警嘅所作所為"},{"pid":"fd71fb1fd72949466cf37c90c4b614dca30556af","tid":2011040,"uid":320192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T17:45:24.000Z","msg":"雪糕筒 Airbnb 自導自演 僭建 冰毒 曲解法律"},{"pid":"cb05a95850d5ffb9e4cea2f3ddba4399ea4867f8","tid":2011040,"uid":10679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T17:46:57.000Z","msg":"母親節係5月10"},{"pid":"a1ae5484370566396beeedc4012afb536e47b0f3","tid":2011040,"uid":200641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb05a95850d5ffb9e4cea2f3ddba4399ea4867f8","tid":2011040,"uid":10679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T17:46:57.000Z","msg":"母親節係5月10"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T17:47:33.000Z","msg":"Sorr<br />\n嬲得滯"},{"pid":"0aab1d0d5cb3132b61b1aaba73c376d45c5e327d","tid":2011040,"uid":229920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T17:48:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2500fe2e0667c8e76241e73b740e2e9efb98835d","tid":2011040,"uid":153496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T17:51:22.000Z","msg":"從今日起，香港嘅母親節因為黑警而多咗一層意義。今日嘅嚴重程度拍得住721同831。"},{"pid":"e6cbee8fd01b3b66618f3329b199a9f85f6a97d0","tid":2011040,"uid":74278,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"repl